Upgrade neo4j-driver to 1.1.1

- Try to auto discover bolt host
  - If fail, assume defaultBoltHost
- Try to connect to it with empty creds
  - If success, execute initCmd
- If fail, look for stored creds and try them
  - If success, execute initCmd
- If fail, execute :server connect
  - If connect with entered creds success, execute initCmd
  - If connect fail, display error message
  - If fail because of expired creds, show change-pw form
- When pw change success, execute initCmd
